::Feline::

She sighed warmly and lifted her head to look around, putting it all 
to memory.  

She smiled and looked at the drink dispencer. "Hmmm, what would you 
like to drink?" she said in a soft, sweet voice."I just would love 
some water, cool water sounds delisous right now."
She purred and brushed the tip of her tail against his neck and now 
up along his ear and over to his cheek, back to the back of his neck.
She still held onto his arm with both of hers and purred.  

With her being this close to him, he should be able to feel the soft 
vibrations of her purring, not just hearing it. She smiled and rubbed 
her head against his shoulder.  She was pleased with herself.
